### Record keyword

- All fields are private and [[SWEN221/SWEN Post-it Model#^c37b3f\|SWEN Post-it Model#^c37b3f]]

```java

{
	public String greet(String other){
		return "Hi " +other+ " I'm " + this.name;
	}
}
```
